T1  - Exploring start-up event sequences
AU  - Carter, Nancy M.
AU  - Gartner, William B.
AU  - Reynolds, Paul D.
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 11
IS  - 3
SP  - 151
EP  - 166
PY  - 1996
DA  - 1996/05/01/
